name: The Wheel of Fortune
description: The Wheel of Fortune spins endlessly, as if to convey that life is made up of both good and bad times, and that we have no control over the cycle. It is something that both kings and workers are subjected to, and it is something that no one on the planet can avoid. When good things happen in your life, make the most of them, because what comes up must always go down. The opposite is also true: when you are in a bad situation, things will eventually improve.
